  <LegalLayout title="Privacy Policy" lastUpdated="November 20, 2025">
    <p>Golden Fox LLC ("we," "us," "our," or "Company") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile game Guns & Fury ("Game" or "Service").</p>

    <p>By using the Game, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with this Privacy Policy, please do not use the Game.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

    <h3>1.1 Information You Provide</h3>
    <p>We may collect the following information that you voluntarily provide:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username, email address (if provided through social login), and profile information</li>
      <li><strong>Social Media Information:</strong> If you connect through social media services (Google, Facebook, Twitter), we may receive your name, email address, profile picture, and other information you permit those services to share</li>
      <li><strong>Communications:</strong> Messages you send to customer support or other communications with us</li>
      <li><strong>User-Generated Content:</strong> Usernames, profile customizations, and in-game messages</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>1.2 Information Collected Automatically</h3>
    <p>When you use the Game, we automatically collect certain information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, device identifiers (IDFA on iOS, AAID on Android), screen resolution, device language</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Game progress, gameplay statistics, features used, session duration, time and date of access, in-game actions and events</li>
      <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, mobile carrier, browser type, crashes and errors, performance metrics</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising IDs:</strong> Mobile advertising identifiers for serving personalized advertisements</li>
      <li><strong>Approximate Location:</strong> Country and region derived from IP address (we do not collect precise geolocation)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>1.3 Information from Third-Party Services</h3>
    <p>We use third-party services that may collect information about you. These services include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Analytics Services:</strong> Google Analytics, Firebase Analytics, Unity Analytics, Game Analytics</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising Networks:</strong> AdMob (Google), Unity Ads, AppLovin, Vungle, AdColony</li>
      <li><strong>Backend Services:</strong> PlayFab (Microsoft)</li>
      <li><strong>Social Login Services:</strong> Google, Facebook, Twitter</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Provide and Maintain the Game:</strong> Enable gameplay, multiplayer features, account management, and save your progress</li>
      <li><strong>Process Transactions:</strong> Process in-app purchases through Apple App Store or Google Play Store</li>
      <li><strong>Improve the Game:</strong> Analyze usage patterns, identify bugs, optimize performance, and develop new features</li>
      <li><strong>Personalize Experience:</strong> Customize game content, difficulty, and recommendations based on your gameplay</li>
      <li><strong>Serve Advertisements:</strong> Display relevant ads and measure ad effectiveness</li>
      <li><strong>Customer Support:</strong> Respond to your requests, questions, and provide technical support</li>
      <li><strong>Security and Fraud Prevention:</strong> Detect and prevent cheating, unauthorized access, and fraudulent activity</li>
      <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Comply with legal obligations and enforce our Terms of Service</li>
      <li><strong>Communications:</strong> Send you game updates, notifications, and promotional materials (with your consent where required)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
    <p>If you are in the European Economic Area (EEA), UK, or Switzerland, we process your personal data under the following legal bases:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Consent:</strong> You have given explicit consent for processing your personal data for specific purposes (e.g., personalized advertising)</li>
      <li><strong>Contract Performance:</strong> Processing is necessary to provide the Game and fulfill our Terms of Service</li>
      <li><strong>Legitimate Interests:</strong> Processing is necessary for our legitimate interests (e.g., improving the Game, fraud prevention, security) and does not override your fundamental rights</li>
      <li><strong>Legal Obligation:</strong> Processing is necessary to comply with applicable laws</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
    <p>We may share your information in the following circumstances:</p>

    <h3>4.1 Service Providers</h3>
    <p>We share information with third-party service providers who perform services on our behalf:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Analytics Providers:</strong> Google Analytics, Firebase, Unity Analytics, Game Analytics</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising Partners:</strong> AdMob, Unity Ads, AppLovin, Vungle, AdColony</li>
      <li><strong>Cloud Services:</strong> PlayFab/Microsoft (for backend services, data storage, and account management)</li>
      <li><strong>Payment Processors:</strong> Apple and Google (for in-app purchase processing)</li>
